{"tid":713617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入獄前拍定片　游蕙禎呼籲大家咪氣餒","createTime":"2018-06-23T03:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T05:05:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2577134477857715ceb87f33c79dad2f238a53","tid":713617,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180623/20429369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20429369&d=owNX%2F0zj4n2GIKLihvuivxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=854d3bfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20429369&h=d2cb49cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180623/20429369</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月23日 <br />\n<br />\n入獄前拍定片　游蕙禎呼籲大家咪氣餒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n青年新政梁頌恆和游蕙禎在前年11月立法會宣誓風波中被控非法集結罪受審，其中游蕙禎放棄上訴入獄四周。青年新政發佈一條游蕙禎入獄前的短片，她表示雖然近年政治打壓越來越嚴重，但寄語港人不要氣餒，並應從不同的方法去支持抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n片段中游蕙禎第一句便指「相信大家見到呢條片嘅時候我已經入獄」，並指近年有不少人因為政治事件而被判入獄，可能會「覺得好氣餒，諗緊點解大家要堅持落去」，但她認為仍然有人默默為香港付出，堅信終點不會一朝一夕到達，希望大家積極參與抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n除了抗爭運動外，市民也可對地區組織作支援，甚至只是將信念與家人分享，擴闊人與資源的網絡，令自己強大起來。對於自己入獄，她不諱言：「既然不能避免，就當作係一種磨練。」希望出獄後能趕上大家繼續堅持抗爭的步伐。<br />\n<br />\n短片連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2yy9ZHz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yy9ZHz&d=owNX%2F0zj4n2GIKLihvuivxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=3f4cca21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2yy9ZHz</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n涉向官掟銀　婦稱無悔<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【罕見異象】兩星期3次水龍捲！破盡6月紀錄"},{"pid":"951dc44b9ff3cbb2ac89b5abfebc1ac50a92dc57","tid":713617,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596205cbe1f132a8870baf66ac70ec06ed174cf8","tid":713617,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb098e05b5e50aa5db11de9f2a8bc3acd28e5b3e","tid":713617,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"除衫先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}